{"tid":1386974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"到而家香港人都仲覺得有險可守","createTime":"2019-07-30T12:31:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T15:12:44.000Z","uid":81236,"like":123,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"889f376e76cc02943c5e1d3043e2918dcb3ba97a","tid":1386974,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:31:48.000Z","msg":"以前就泛民覺得只要有立法會否決權就無問題<br />\n<br />\n到後來未入閘既政治審查，到後來選到都比人無理DQ，既保皇黨變成大多數強行通過先醒覺<br />\n<br />\n而家就話仲有陪審團否決權可以守<br />\n如果仲得既梁天琦就唔會入獄啦<br />\n到底香港人仲要比人呃多幾次，或者自己幻想三權分立有效運作？<br />\n<br />\n一次又一次搬龍門變到要靠陪審否決權同三峽由抵擋萬年一遇變成不可靠有咩分別？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">到底你地幾時先肯醒？從來呢啲說話都係用黎減少市民反彈</span></span>"},{"pid":"af1530562756501bd4dac2b836b1c89023c9b144","tid":1386974,"uid":81236,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:33:35.000Z","msg":"到正式審決就話不能完全倚賴陪審否決權，真係好醜陋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4baf8242b9288deffa3049692237e2f719947735","tid":1386974,"uid":81236,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:35:11.000Z","msg":"到時可能又有人係法院偷拍，比壓力陪審團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n劇本一早就寫好"},{"pid":"b0e8275c6b0b2f4a41239735c0421b7914d00c21","tid":1386974,"uid":81236,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:37:53.000Z","msg":"你地認清現實未？"},{"pid":"381798e0a5a2b867646c7fb4daf9fe41d1d060eb","tid":1386974,"uid":81236,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:41:38.000Z","msg":"到審判既時候就會有人放風，減少人既期望落差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到而家香港人都仲想淨係靠險要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />覺得會幫你伸張正義"},{"pid":"045e61b5c8aab9e89023c6d05eb5e3a990528df4","tid":1386974,"uid":56157,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:42:21.000Z","msg":"話長期抗爭班人<br />\n由97到依家廿幾年了，長到幾時?<br />\n係未來監控燈柱，信用系統等緊你地<br />\n現在，警察既氣炎已不斷加大，隨街可以要求一般市民口罩都唔準帶<br />\n四名示威者因絕望而自殺。在此之前仲有百幾名學生自殺<br />\n<br />\n你同我講留得青山在？"},{"pid":"1a9f6b1de5e1c9b1054bf8be7cdc6e1f3881130a","tid":1386974,"uid":81236,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:45:47.000Z","msg":"同你地講仲有路可行<br />\n<br />\n實際就比條愈黎愈窄既路你地行<br />\n<br />\n等之後再有人被控你地都覺得無咩野<br />\n<br />\n你問心果句覺得真係冇事？"},{"pid":"ae234a5825990e8775b037dd6d1321fb7dd593e0","tid":1386974,"uid":81236,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"045e61b5c8aab9e89023c6d05eb5e3a990528df4","tid":1386974,"uid":56157,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:42:21.000Z","msg":"話長期抗爭班人<br />\n由97到依家廿幾年了，長到幾時?<br />\n係未來監控燈柱，信用系統等緊你地<br />\n現在，警察既氣炎已不斷加大，隨街可以要求一般市民口罩都唔準帶<br />\n四名示威者因絕望而自殺。在此之前仲有百幾名學生自殺<br />\n<br />\n你同我講留得青山在？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:48:28.000Z","msg":"到底要比人呃多幾多年？<br />\n係你地身上拎走幾多野？<br />\n<br />\n你地對唔對得住為左喚醒香港人而死諫既人？"},{"pid":"7de436981250c6b80e46057a3d7469307d7cc196","tid":1386974,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:53:06.000Z","msg":"就算功能組別過半都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca7482be4aa7650fbb9abf3bc6410d595b575ab5","tid":1386974,"uid":81236,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:53:07.000Z","msg":"仲要話100%救得返？<br />\n<br />\n我唔係要散播失敗主義<br />\n而係希望喚醒你地<br />\n唔好再係安慰既語言中生存<br />\n<br />\n只有站出來先可以救得返<br />\n靠既唔係人地<br />\n靠既係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">果個就係你</span></span>"},{"pid":"63ba53364571a04815ec67dbc74fd4f4c25876f8","tid":1386974,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:56:27.000Z","msg":"唔想再比人呃既<br />\n唔好網上話我知你訓醒未<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">出黎話比我知</span></span>"},{"pid":"78f0349bb4587bc670155f68220f2a328cc91e9a","tid":1386974,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:59:39.000Z","msg":"仲要有幾多既野係你身上流走？<br />\n幾多人命係你手中失去？"},{"pid":"5aaff8080fe1ff3532555873d563e38ba57443a5","tid":1386974,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:07:03.000Z","msg":"4條人命係唔係都唔夠喚醒你睇清政治既醜惡？制度既漏洞？"},{"pid":"c12de40c06d2898463cb8aeb0eb5c8ef79099c48","tid":1386974,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:09:06.000Z","msg":"一步一步咁迫你<br />\n而家想迫死你地<br />\n你地仲要話有生路"},{"pid":"8d6c54547b4299e635bd8407409c453403034f07","tid":1386974,"uid":54930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:11:00.000Z","msg":"有險可守❌<br />\n有錢係手✔<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e53ace9534b7cd3037b355553ab5babecafd3a4f","tid":1386974,"uid":175623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:13:29.000Z","msg":"求互推<br />\n[抛磚引玉] 所有連登軍師, 文宣入, (好認真!!)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dtfNgS\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dtfNgS</a>"},{"pid":"8756984cb7c248450db968be6263aa86dcc5c96d","tid":1386974,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:15:43.000Z","msg":"訓醒未？"},{"pid":"583bde061a52218bd34ada8805081c1d8703a814","tid":1386974,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:16:11.000Z","msg":"自我安慰夠未？"},{"pid":"832dc34b736d9f002db43f6e5c46f4ad5444e688","tid":1386974,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:16:33.000Z","msg":"肯出黎未？"},{"pid":"33b62451d953d8597671b41617c076ef9d949f9f","tid":1386974,"uid":284317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:18:59.000Z","msg":"冇大罷工就一定輸<br />\n成年人爭住買贖罪券都唔肯罷幾日工既話<br />\n今次抗爭就走到盡頭<br />\n勇武俾人拉晒<br />\n大家做番港豬繼續番工"},{"pid":"ff9f4f1dab55942b0f981e734d078451b98b887f","tid":1386974,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:20:02.00